            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="feature-card">
            <span class="feature-icon">üéØ</span>
            <h3>Deal Alerts</h3>
            <p>
              Set up alerts for specific products and get notified when they go
              on sale.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          &copy; 2024 Grocery Price Checker. Helping you save money on groceries
          across the UK.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
